<span id="freeTextContainer16842227560828257475"><i>
  <b>“I am a dreamer. I know so little of real life that I just can&apos;t help re-living such moments as these in my dreams, for such moments are something I have very rarely experienced. I am going to dream about you the whole night, the whole week, the whole year. I feel I know you so well that I couldn&apos;t have known you better if we&apos;d been friends for twenty years. You won&apos;t fail me, will you? Only two minutes, and you&apos;ve made me happy forever. Yes, happy. Who knows, perhaps you&apos;ve reconciled me wit</b></i></span>
  <span id="freeText16842227560828257475" style="display:none"><i>
  <b>“I am a dreamer. I know so little of real life that I just can't help re-living such moments as these in my dreams, for such moments are something I have very rarely experienced. I am going to dream about you the whole night, the whole week, the whole year. I feel I know you so well that I couldn't have known you better if we'd been friends for twenty years. You won't fail me, will you? Only two minutes, and you've made me happy forever. Yes, happy. Who knows, perhaps you've reconciled me with myself, resolved all my doubts.''</b>
