<div id="review_2361110282" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2361110282" />
    <a title="Laurene" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3628266-laurene"><img alt="Laurene" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1487357434p2/3628266.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2361110282?book_show_action=true">Apr 18, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Laurene" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Laurene" href="/user/show/3628266-laurene">Laurene</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2361110282" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5087816877213684349">This novel is wonderfully written. The flow, the imagery and the character development. The main character claims he is too shy to get into a relationship -- &quot;And I do nothing but dream every day that at last I shall meet someone. Oh, if only you knew how often I have been in love that way. With an ideal, with the one I dream of in my sleep.&quot; Who doesn&apos;t dream of the &quot;someone&quot; coming into a person&apos;s life. And the chance to experience the relationship with that &quot;someone&quot;. &quot;May your sky be clear, </span>
  <span id="freeText5087816877213684349" style="display:none">This novel is wonderfully written. The flow, the imagery and the character development. The main character claims he is too shy to get into a relationship -- "And I do nothing but dream every day that at last I shall meet someone. Oh, if only you knew how often I have been in love that way. With an ideal, with the one I dream of in my sleep." Who doesn't dream of the "someone" coming into a person's life. And the chance to experience the relationship with that "someone". "May your sky be clear, may your sweet smile be bright and untroubled, and may you be blessed for that moment of blissful happiness which you gave to another, lonely and grateful heart!"</span>
  <a data-text-id="5087816877213684349" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

